txt.en: Faeron can be found outside Kala-gijak.\n\nYou should talk to Faeron.
'I have heard that the Uruks drink a nasty brew that lessens their inhibitions, making them more ferocious fighters. Destroy any barrels that you come across before they can consume more.'
'Ugh, I can smell the brew's stench from here. Thank you for taking care of that. We do not want the Uruks to gain any advantages in combat.'
Uruk brew barrels can be found in Kala-gijak.\n\nYou should destroy Uruk brew barrels.
The Uruks have many barrels of brew in Kala-gijak,. This brew makes them more irritable and fight harder. Faeron thinks it is a good idea to destroy these barrels.
